text.tspan: Three main user types for your projects

tspan.tspan: Personas are fictional characters, which you create based upon
your research in order to represent the different user types.
Use cases help you to think about who will be using the design
and focuses on features that will engage and give users value.
Decide who your users are and prioritize them in order of
importance. You may have less or more key users, so feel free
to adjust the number of users.
